22:73.occasion:
. He also mentioned the scheme of the deities and compared it to cobweb. Upon
hearing this, they said: 'See how Allah mentions gnats and spiders in the Qur'an revealed to Muhammad;
what is the use of this?' And so Allah revealed this”.

